strings.Value: "The Narlmarches is no place for a little boy. Too many dangers."
"I wonder what's hidden in the heart of these swamps... Will we ever know?"
"Keep your spirits up, Ekun. Soon we'll come to the unfortunate child's rescue."
"He'll be all right, you'll see! Children aren't nearly as helpless as some adults â€” and they often think much faster."
